{"tid":1745321,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於鄭文傑BBC訪問 有一點諗唔明","createTime":"2019-11-22T07:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T15:04:19.000Z","uid":314354,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b12f461c192b763594205d5945b46e0996eed5","tid":1745321,"uid":314354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GNqtktbjTk4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGNqtktbjTk4&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=b764d9ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GNqtktbjTk4</a><br />\n<br />\n去到最後一段<br />\n主持人: 咁你有冇嫖過妓<br />\nCheng: 我哋唔應該注視喺呢件事上面，因為咁樣會中咗中國嘅圈套，但我想喺度澄清，我冇做過任何會令我愛同重視嘅人後悔嘅事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我諗唔明點解會跌入中國圈套</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭文傑咁樣答，我覺得個核彈嘅威力會<span style=\"color: pink;\">弱咗</span><br />\n(俾我感覺有啲似當年嘅克林頓，佢單性醜聞未俾人篤爆之前就係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[戴返好個頭盔先]<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論鄭文傑有冇做過，呢件事依然都係核彈，因為始終佢係入面都受到不人道對待同酷刑<br />\n<br />\n小弟只係想學術討論，Simon Cheng有冇做過其實唔重要"},{"pid":"c49a1e6d9aaaf39fd0d4e9181c77e2d5ef63e603","tid":1745321,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"因為係有去邪骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b20f3057c8922228dc6b867681d24cfe5ef9b3","tid":1745321,"uid":261332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:20:08.000Z","msg":"咁你都唔明<br />\n而家問題重點係中共酷刑虐待，應該討論嘅係佢哋究竟仲收埋咗幾多人。<br />\n<br />\n而唔係跟佢哋轉移視線嘅劇本走，一個二個走去做cctv偵探研究佢有冇叫雞....."},{"pid":"71d60a123170dfca303839ca058645a95dafe4d0","tid":1745321,"uid":314354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52b20f3057c8922228dc6b867681d24cfe5ef9b3","tid":1745321,"uid":261332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy